      <div class="reviews__global" aria-label="Note globale Google : 5 sur 5, 6 avis">
        <div class="reviews__stars" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="reviews__global-text"><strong>5/5</strong> — 6 avis Google vérifiés</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="reviews__grid" role="list">
      <li class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card__stars" aria-label="5 étoiles" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="review-card__text">
          "Très satisfaite des travaux réalisés dans notre jardin.
          Ponctualité et rapidité dans l'exécution des travaux.
          Je le recommande sans hésiter."
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="review-card__author">
          <span class="review-card__name">Véronique V.</span>
          <time class="review-card__date" datetime="2026-03">mai 2025</time>
        </footer>
      </li>
      <li class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card__stars" aria-label="5 étoiles" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="review-card__text">
          "Très contents du travail réalisé. Olivier est un paysagiste professionnel, à l'écoute et intarissable ! Nous avons fait appel à lui, suite aux bons avis de nos voisins, pour l'élagage dans notre jardin que nous avons acquis à l'abandon : travail impeccable ! J'ai aussi pu bénéficier de ses précieux conseils lors d'une séance de coaching : j'espère pouvoir les reproduire ! À contacter sans hésiter !"
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="review-card__author">
          <span class="review-card__name">Andrea 0.</span>
          <time class="review-card__date" datetime="2026-02">janvier 2022</time>
        </footer>
      </li>
      <li class="review-card">
        <div class="review-card__stars" aria-label="5 étoiles" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="18" height="18"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <blockquote class="review-card__text">
          "Il nous a fait un aménagement de terrain complet suite à une construction.
          Nous sommes très content de lui avoir confié notre projet car le résultat est parfait.
          Merci beaucoup encore pour ton travail et ton professionnalisme."
        </blockquote>
        <footer class="review-card__author">
          <span class="review-card__name">Caroline L.</span>
          <time class="review-card__date" datetime="2026-01">mars 2020</time>
        </footer>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews {
    background: var(--color-primary-dark);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: calc(var(--space-xl) + 60px) 0 calc(var(--space-xl) + 50px);
    position: relative;
  }

  .reviews::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 65px;
    background: var(--color-white);
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 35%, 0 100%);
  }

  .reviews::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 55px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    clip-path: polygon(0 65%, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
  }

  .reviews__header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .reviews__header .section-label {
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  .reviews__title {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .reviews__global {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .reviews__stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  .reviews__global-text {
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
  }

  .reviews__global-text strong {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .reviews__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .review-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    transition: background-color var(--transition), transform var(--transition);
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .review-card__stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
  }

  .review-card__text {
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-style: italic;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .review-card__author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .review-card__name {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .review-card__date {
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .reviews__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .reviews__global {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
